in the second quarter of 2012, we committed to sell a portion of our business properties portfolio (business property) in real estate, including certain commercial loans, the origination and servicing platforms and the servicing rights on loans previously securitized by gecc. we completed the sale ofbusiness property on october 1, 2012 for proceeds of $2,406 million. we deconsolidated substantially all real estate securitization entities in the fourth quarter of 2012 as servicing rights related to these entities were transferred to the buyer at closing.
